Some_Verant_Designer_02 said at the last Fan fair that VI hates Main Tank Stratagies and are working at getting around that.<br>
<br>
&lt;&gt;Enter Fights with multiple unmez'able guards - now you just have Uber MT1, and several designated 2ndary MTs.<br>
&lt;&gt;Enter the addition of more mobs with Teleport abilities (Griegs, for instance).  Can't MT when you Get TP'd out.  Grats Dumn Zergling Pure DPS tactics (or Strange &quot;time the TP, make useless class gain aggro and suck up the TP&quot; tactics).<br>
&lt;&gt;Enter the return of Death Touches.  Like TP, But lasts longer.  Grats Dumn Zergling Pure DPS Tactics (or Strange &quot;time the DT, make useless class gain aggro and suck up the DT&quot; tactics).<br>
<br>
Remember kiddies, if you arn't Zerg'ing, you're exploiting!<br>
